    "Limitations in current governance in addressing AI sustainability risks were also highlighted.",
    "Prioritizing SDG 6 (Clean Water and Sanitation), Doorn [18] emphasized the relatively underdeveloped usage of AI techniques in the water domain and the need for attempts to develop insights about 'responsible AI. '",
    "The literature review identified four application categories, viz.",
    "modeling, prediction and forecasting, decision support and operational management, and optimization.",
    "Three insights were provided, like the general use of AI, multi-objective optimization (ensure pluralism and dynamism of values), and the use of theory-guided data science."
  ],
